quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,104,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Yemwe bantu! Niba mushidikanya ku idini ryanjye, (mumenye ko) ntazigera ngaragira ibyo mugaragira bitari Allah. Ahubwo ngaragira Allah We ubambura ubuzima, kandi nategetswe kuba umwe mu bemera.”"
  10,105,"(Naranahishuriwe nti) “Unashikame ku idini (Isilamu) ugaragira Allah wenyine, kandi uramenye ntuzabe mu babangikanyamana.”"
  10,106,"“Kandi ntukagire undi usaba utari Allah, utagira icyo akumarira cyangwa ngo agire icyo agutwara. Nuramuka ubikoze, mu by’ukuri ubwo uzaba ubaye mu babangikanyamana.”"
  10,107,"Kandi Allah aramutse aguteje ingorane, nta wazigukiza utari We, ndetse anagushakiye icyiza, nta wakumira ingabire ze agenera uwo ashaka mu bagaragu be. Kandi ni We Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimpuhwe"
  10,108,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Yemwe bantu! Rwose mwagezweho n’ukuri guturutse kwa Nyagasani wanyu. Bityo, uyobotse aba yigiriye neza ndetse n’uyobye aba yihemukiye. Kandi njye si ndi umuhagararizi wanyu (sinoherejwe kugira ngo mbahatire kuyoboka).”"
  10,109,"Kandi ujye ukurikiza ibyo uhishurirwa, unihangane kugeza ubwo Allah abakiranuye (wowe na bo), kuko ari We Mukiranuzi mwiza"